# GHC Extension: OverloadedStrings

{-# LANGUAGE OverloadedStrings #-}

### All Numeric Literals are Polymorphic over the

~~~ {.haskell}
a :: Int
a = 7

b :: Integer
b = 255

c :: Float
c = 5
~~~

### Problem: String Literals are non Polymorphic, Always String

~~~ {.haskell}
s1 :: String
s1 = "I'm a String"

s2 :: Text
s2 = "I'm a Text"            -- compiles only with OverloadedStrings
~~~

### Note: The IsString Typeclass is used
